overview: From 2026-01-04 to 2026-01-11, elizaos-plugins/plugin-rolodex had 0 new PRs (0 merged), 0 new issues, and 5 active contributors.

Their work this week primarily centered on critical bug fixes and configuration management, significantly improving system stability and developer workflow efficiency.
